snippet.title: SSK: SAGE Promo missing link
snippet.description:
Visit http://supersonicknockout.x10.mx/ for new updates.

This gameplay video was supposed to be used in the promo video of SAGE 2007, which be viewed on episode 8 of The Sonic Show.

Due to some problem or something the footage was unable to make it to the promo, so I'm bringing it on here and my site instead XD.
